### Generate Payload GraphQL Schema with pnpm

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/graphql/graphql-schema.mdx

This command executes the `generate:schema` script from the `@payloadcms/graphql` package, creating a GraphQL schema based on your Payload collections and globals. The schema is typically output to `schema.graphql` by default, or `./graphql/schema.graphql` if a custom path is configured.

```bash
pnpm payload-graphql generate:schema
```
